Tool.Infrastructures:
Bio-X, Human Frontier Science Program, Howard Hughes Medical Institute, Stanford University;
            California; USA, Packard, Searle Scholar, Microsoft Research, Alfred P. Sloan Foundation, Edward
            Mallinckrodt Jr. Foundation, NIH, DFG

Tool.Description:
Deposition and retrieval network for cryoEM map, model and associated metadata, as well as a portal
            for software tools for standardized map format conversion, map, segmentation and model assessment,
            visualization, and data integration.
